{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-error-message-component","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 11","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Trenutno je element <code>div</code> postavljen u gornji levi ugao ekrana za pregled. Ali bilo bi lepo dodati malo prostora na vrh elementa. Da biste primenili <code>margin</code>, na element koji koristi Tailwind CSS, možete koristiti sledeći obrazac: <code>m-number</code>, gde <code>number</code> predstavlja fiksne piksele za primenu na sve četiri strane.</p>\n<p>Ako želite da primenite margina samo na jednu stranu, možete koristiti bilo koji od sledećih obrazaca: <code>mt-number</code> (margin top), <code>mb-number</code> (margin bottom), <code>mr-number</code> (margin right) i <code>ml-number</code> (margin left).</p>\n<p>Evo primera primene <code>margin-bottom</code> na element:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;p class=\"mb-8\">This is margin.&#x3C;/p>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar vašeg otvarajućeg taga <code>div</code>, koristite odgovarajuću utilitarnu klasu za primenu <code>margin-top</code> od <code>4px</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"684d09cad4ec900e41db2e74","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-11"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Error Message Component</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"bg-red-100 border-2 border-red-300 rounded-md md:w-1/2 p-4\">\n      <p>\n        <strong>Error!</strong> Something went wrong. Please try again.\n      </p>\n      <button aria-label=\"Dismiss\">\n        <span aria-hidden>&times;</span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[9,11],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš otvarajući <code>div</code> tag treba da ima utiliteti <code>mt-4</code> za class.</p>","testString":"const divEl = document.querySelector(\"div\");\nassert.isTrue(divEl.classList.contains(\"mt-4\"));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/#workshop-error-message-component","dashedName":"step-11","certification":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","chapter":"front-end-development-libraries","module":"css-libraries-and-frameworks","block":"workshop-error-message-component","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-12","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-10","id":"684d09cad4ec900e41db2e74","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Error Message Component</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  </head>\n  <body>  \n    <div class=\"bg-red-100 border-2 border-red-300 rounded-md md:w-1/2 p-4 mt-4